Dark farce about an old man (Jose Isbert) who becomes obsessed with having a motorized wheelchair. Pedro Porcel. Alvarito: Jose Luis Lopez Vazquez. Matilde: Luisa Ponte. Luces: Lepe. Hilario: Antonio Gavilan. Alvarez: Angel Alvarez. A.k.a. "The Wheelchair." Directed and co-scripted by Marco Ferreri.
